Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
"Are you planning to rent out shared coworking office space in Indore for your startup? Join Incuspaze Co-Working office in Ushaganj. Located at Apollo Premier, Plot no. 1, Commercial House, Godhra Highway, Ushaganj. Incuspaze provides a premium office space with state of the art facilities without breaking the bank. By virtue of being in the business city, you will be where all the action is and won’t miss anything that happens in the startup community.

If you are a startup, freelancer, blogger or an enterprise – we are sure you will love Incuspaze, not just for the energy but also the doors of opportunity that it will open for you. We understand what startups require to grow their business and that’s what makes us a one-stop solution for all your startup needs"
